<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>16</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thil mak sut senloh ka Pathien,
 Na sep tincheng mak ka sau hi;
 Himahleh Na lungsietna chuh,
 Thil dang cheng sang in mak ka sau (2)

[V2]
 Nangmah bang in mi kuo-a um?
 Nei ngaidam zel in Nei na deih (2)

[V3]
 2. Gitloh huoisie ngaidam ding a,
 Mawhchangsa kei Nei na hawih hi;
 Na thilhih theihna ahi a,
 Kuoma'n ziechuh a nei puou hi (2)

[V4]
 Nangmah bang in mi kuo-a um?
 Nei ngaidam zel in Nei na deih (2)

[V5]
 3. Beimang nung hi lawp a, ling in,
 Pathien ngaihdamna ka chang u'i;
 Gitloh simsen loh ngaihdamna,
 Isu thisan a chawksa kha (2)

[V6]
 Nangmah bang in mi kuo-a um?
 Nei ngaidam zel in Nei na deih (2)

[V7]
 4. Aw, lungsietna gensen loh chuh,
 Pathien thilhih mak ahi a;
 A pakna chun khawvel dim hen,
 Van a Angelte lasak tawh.

[V8]
 Nangmah bang in mi kuo-a um?
 Nei ngaidam zel in Nei na deih (2)</lyrics>
<title>HUDDERSFLIED</title>
</song>